#!/bin/bash
#
# GRID-INIT
##
## Start/Stop Services
##
##		1. SGE Deamons
##
##		2. Keyless Login between Nodes
##
##		3. Mount Shared File Systems for Management & Job Execution
##	

##		TESTING
